<text top="300" left="77" width="236" height="16" font="0"><b>Validation 1: Immunoblot Analysis  </b></text>
<text top="326" left="77" width="467" height="13" font="2">For an antibody to meet ENCODE validation standards, a single band of the predicted </text>
<text top="340" left="77" width="467" height="13" font="2">size,  or  a  band  of  no  less  than  half  the  total  signal,  must  be  detected  in  a  lane  on  a </text>
<text top="354" left="77" width="74" height="13" font="2">Western blot. </text>
<text top="378" left="77" width="3" height="13" font="2"> </text>
<text top="401" left="77" width="187" height="13" font="1"><b>a.  Vendor immunoblot analysis  </b></text>
